'''硒氰'''是一种[[拟卤素|拟卤素]]，化学式为(SeCN)<sub>2</sub>。它可由[[硒氰酸银|硒氰酸银]]和[[碘|碘]]在[[乙醚|乙醚]]中反应得到，其中86%的碘会转化为[[碘化银|碘化银]]：<ref name=Walden>{{cite journal|journal=Chemical Reviews|volume=5|issue=3|language=en|issn=0009-2665|date=1928-10-01|pages=339–359|doi=10.1021/cr60019a002|url=https://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/cr60019a002|title=Free Inorganic Radicals.|accessdate=2021-01-04|author=P. Walden, L. F. Audrieth}}</ref>
: 2 AgSeCN + I<sub>2</sub> {{eqm}} 2 AgI + (SeCN)<sub>2</sub>

它在水中按下式水解：<ref name=Walden />
: 2 (SeCN)<sub>2</sub> + 3 H<sub>2</sub>O → H<sub>2</sub>SeO<sub>3</sub> + 3 HSeCN + HCN

缓慢加热硒氰，它可以歧化为[[:d:Q72507295|二氰化硒]]（Se(CN)<sub>2</sub>）和[[二硒氰酸硒|二硒氰酸硒]]（Se(SeCN)<sub>2</sub>）。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Inorganic Chemistry|volume=45|issue=2|language=en|issn=0020-1669|date=2006-01|pages=710–716|doi=10.1021/ic0515103|url=https://pubs.acs.org/doi/10.1021/ic0515103|title=E 2 (CN) 2 (E = S, Se) and Related Compounds|accessdate=2021-01-04|author=Colin J. Burchell, Petr Kilian, Alexandra M. Z. Slawin, J. Derek Woollins, Karla Tersago, Christian Van Alsenoy, Frank Blockhuys}}</ref>

它和[[三苯基膦|三苯基膦]]反应，可以得到Ph<sub>3</sub>P(SeCN)<sub>2</sub><ref>{{cite journal|journal=Tetrahedron Letters|volume=20|issue=24|language=en|date=1979-01|pages=2251–2252|doi=10.1016/S0040-4039(01)93689-5|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0040403901936895|title=Selenocyanation using a combined reagent of triphenylphosphine and selenocyanogen. A new and simple synthesis of alkyl selenocyanates and symmetrical alkyl diselenides from alcohols|accessdate=2021-01-04|author=Y. Tamura, M. Adachi, T. Kawasaki, Y. Kita}}</ref>；和二羰基二茂钛反应，羰基被取代，得到(C<sub>5</sub>H<sub>5</sub>)<sub>2</sub>Ti(NCSe)<sub>2</sub>；和[[二茂铬|二茂铬]]或[[二茂钒|二茂钒]]反应，分别得到(C<sub>5</sub>H<sub>5</sub>)<sub>2</sub>Cr(NCSe)(SeCN)和(C<sub>5</sub>H<sub>5</sub>)<sub>2</sub>V(NCSe)<sub>2</sub>。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of Organometallic Chemistry|volume=165|issue=2|language=en|date=1979-01|pages=215–223|doi=10.1016/S0022-328X(00)94323-7|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0022328X00943237|title=Synthesis and characterization of mixed cyanothiocyanate and cyanoselenocyanate complexes of bis(cyclopentadienyl)-titanium, -vanadium and -chromium|accessdate=2021-01-04|author=M. Morán, V. Fernández|archive-date=2018-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612215004/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0022328X00943237|dead-url=no}}</ref>它和CN<sup>−</sup>在[[乙腈|乙腈]]中反应，生成SeCN<sup>−</sup>和Se(CN)<sub>2</sub>。<ref>Austad, Tor. Reaction between dithio- or selenocyanide and the cyanide ion in acetonitrile.  Study of the mechanism using ionic carbon-​13 labeled cyanide. ''Acta Chemica Scandinavica, Series A:  Physical and Inorganic Chemistry'', 1974. 28 (7): 806-808. ISSN: 0302-4377.</ref>

